title: Wallx - Wallpaper Pack v3.2 APK (Android)
description:
Wallx is a wallpaper pack. It includes all the wallpapers from all my icon packs in a single app.
The wallpapers included in this pack are original, unique and designed by scratch. The nature/landscape wallpapers are photographed myself.

Features:
Cloud based 1018 Wallpapers to match the icons. All walls are around 2-20mb in size. Please be patient while it downloads and applies.
Dashboard application for easy wallpaper apply with cropping function.
Muzei Live Wallpaper support.
Multi Device resolution supported. The app will correctly crop and apply the wallpaper in full quality as per your device.
Future Updates: New wallpapers will be added as and when new icon packs gets released. Each new icon pack release normally has around 50-100 new walls.
What's in this version : (Updated : Dec 1, 2015)
Changes as per new Google Guidelines
Performance Improvements
Android 6.0 Marshmallow Support
Required Android O/S : 4.0.3+
